Description: A high-performance, tidyverse-style interface to vehicle routing
    problem (VRP) solving. Ports the PyVRP C++ core to R via cpp11, with no
    Python runtime dependency. Supports capacitated VRP, time windows, multiple
    depots, heterogeneous fleets and prize-collecting variants, driven by an
    iterated local search metaheuristic.
